Package view

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    CoffeeController
    CoffeeController class handles inputs from the ordering Coffee GUI and defines all actions and helper methods relating events triggered by the GUI
    DonutController
    DonutController class handles inputs from the ordering donuts GUI and defines all actions and helper methods relating to events triggered by the GUI
    MainMenuController
    MainMenu Controller handles inputs from GUI regarding ordering donuts, ordering coffee, viewing their current order, and viewing store orders
    OrderController
    OrderController is extended by DonutController and Coffee Controller and allows commmunication between the two controller classes
    StoreOrderController
    StoreOrderController handles inputs from the store orders GUI and defines all actions and helper methods relating to events triggered by the GUI such as exporting store orders and removing an order from store orders
    YourOrderController
    YourOrderController class handles inputs from the your order GUI and defines all actions and helper methods relating to events triggered by the GUI
